George Lynch (born September 28, 1954) is an American hard rock guitarist and songwriter. Lynch is best known for his work with the bands Dokken, Lynch Mob, and Souls of We. Lynch is considered to be one of the most influential and famous 80's glam metal and hard rock guitarists. He is known for his unique playing style and sound. He is ranked #47 in "100 greatest guitarists of all time" by Guitar World magazine also rnaked #10 in "Top 10 Metal Guitarists of All Time" by Gibson
